 17 | ## The Problem
 18 | 
 19 | Every developer knows this pain. You spend 30 messages 
 20 | explaining your codebase to an AI, get a partial answer, 
 21 | then start a new session and explain everything again. 
 22 | Forever. On a simple project this is annoying. On a 
 23 | complex multi-system codebase — it costs weeks.
 24 | 
 25 | ## The Solution
 26 | 
 27 | Codebase Brain uses IBM Bob to generate three permanent 
 28 | artifacts that give any complex codebase instant memory:
 29 | 
 30 | | Artifact | What It Does | Size |
 31 | |---|---|---|
 32 | | AGENTS.md | Complete technical brain — architecture, failures, gotchas | 300+ lines |
 33 | | Slash Commands | Domain expert commands any developer can invoke | 2,333 lines |
 34 | | Domain Skill | Makes Bob a senior engineer on your codebase instantly | 545 lines |
