 45 | ## How It Works
 46 | 
 47 | **Step 1** — Point IBM Bob at your repository
 48 | 
 49 | **Step 2** — Bob reads every file and generates AGENTS.md 
 50 | with complete architecture, signal chains, failure modes, 
 51 | and gotchas
